{
  "id": 7598,
  "name": "Furnace Shell Mountain Weasel",
  "desc": "An ancient variant of mountain weasel that has adapted to a unique, Phlogiston-rich environment isolated from the outside world.<br>By consuming creatures rich in Phlogiston, this species accumulates power in the shell it holds. After a prolonged existence in the ruins of the Sacred Mountain, its affinity for Phlogiston seems to have caused it to be influenced by the Source Mechanisms within the ruins, creating a unique symbiotic relationship between them.",
  "icon_url": "https://act-webstatic.hoyoverse.com/event-static-hoyowiki-admin/2025/03/17/de8e675a8d6621783a7784a2c6668049_2984216873026527642.png",
